# Hunyuan-MT-7B — быстрый контур виджета, GPU3, порт 8004 (roadmap § 4.3).
# Изолирован от batch-нагрузки Qwen3: латентность выделения < 2 с.
[Unit]
Description=vLLM Hunyuan-MT-7B (GPU3, :8004)
After=network-online.target
Wants=network-online.target

[Service]
Type=simple
Environment=CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=3
Environment=NCCL_P2P_DISABLE=1
Environment=NCCL_IB_DISABLE=1
Environment=CUDA_HOME=/usr/local/cuda
Environment=PATH=/root/services/vllm-qwen32b/.venv/bin:/usr/local/cuda/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin
# GPU3 — NUMA node1
ExecStart=/usr/bin/numactl --cpunodebind=1 --membind=1 \
    /root/services/vllm-qwen32b/.venv/bin/vllm serve /root/models/Hunyuan-MT-7B \
    --served-model-name hunyuan-mt-7b \
    --host 127.0.0.1 \
    --port 8004 \
    --gpu-memory-utilization 0.85 \
    --max-model-len 8192 \
    --max-num-seqs 64
Restart=always
RestartSec=10
TimeoutStartSec=900
LimitNOFILE=65536

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
